<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Employee Identity Template</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
      html, body {
        height: 100%;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .page {
        position: relative;
        width: 794px;
        height: 1123px;
        padding: 2.5rem;
        background-color: white;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: space-between;
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="page">
      <!-- Header Section -->
      <div>
        <div class="relative border-b-8 border-blue-700 pb-6 mb-10">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <div>
              <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-800 tracking-wide">DOTLABS.AI</h1>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic">Smart. Simple. Scalable.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-right">
              <p class="text-sm">Date: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString() %></p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute left-0 bottom-0 w-40 h-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-800 to-cyan-400 transform -rotate-2"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-700 border-b pb-1 border-blue-500">Employee Information</h2>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-16 gap-y-4">
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-600">Full Name</p>
              <p class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900"><%= Name %></p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-600">Email Address</p>
              <p class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900"><%= Email %></p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-600">Department</p>
              <p class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900"><%= Department %></p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-600">Employee ID</p>
              <p class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">#<%= employeeId %></p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-8 p-6 border-l-4 border-blue-600 bg-blue-50 shadow-sm text-justify space-y-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
            <p><%= Name %> has officially been recognized as a trusted and essential part of Dotlabs.ai. As an active contributor in the <%= Department %> department, their role significantly impacts our mission to build intelligent, user-friendly systems that scale efficiently and adapt quickly to evolving needs in the tech world.</p>

            <p>Joining Dotlabs.ai means more than just being part of a company — it means becoming part of a vision to simplify complexity through technology. With each project and every collaboration, <%= Name %> continues to showcase integrity, commitment, and the ability to think beyond the present. Their email address, <%= Email %>, serves as the direct contact point for innovation and support driven by our standards of excellence.</p>

            <p>This document is a formal acknowledgment of the credibility and responsibility entrusted to <%= Name %>. It is also a symbol of Dotlabs.ai’s gratitude for the consistent performance and passion demonstrated day after day. From internal development to external outreach, <%= Name %> represents the very ideals our organization is proud to uphold.</p>

            <p>As we move into the future of AI and smart systems, Dotlabs.ai is confident that our collective strength lies in people like <%= Name %>. Through integrity, teamwork, and visionary thinking, we continue to push boundaries and lead industries — together.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Bottom Section: QR + Footer -->
      <div class="relative mt-auto pt-10">
        <!-- QR Code Placement -->
        <div class="absolute right-0 bottom-24 text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-1">Scan to verify identity</p>
          <img src="<%= qrCode %>" alt="QR Code" class="w-28 h-28 border-2 border-gray-300 shadow-lg inline-block" />
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <footer class="w-full border-t-8 border-blue-700 pt-4 pb-2 text-center text-sm text-gray-600 bg-white">
          <div class="flex justify-center space-x-10 text-blue-800 font-semibold mb-1">
            <span>www.dotlabs.ai</span>
            <span>carrer@dotlabs.ai</span>
            <span>+123 456 7890</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs">&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Dotlabs.ai. All rights reserved.</p>
        </footer>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
